- Trace analysis focused on components of interest. Non-constant frontend-1 trace series (69 series) show meaningful duration increases to downstream services overlapping the frontend-1 fault interval (07:04–07:07). Many trace.duration_p95/duration_mean series show high breaches during or immediately around that interval.
